'''Ōga Shrine''' (おおがじんじゃ) is a {{ill|lt=shrine|Q845945|WD=Q845945|1=Shinto shrine}} located in Omigami, Naka-ku, {{ill|lt=Okayama|Q200078|WD=Q200078|1=Okayama}}, {{ill|lt=Okayama Prefecture|Q132936|WD=Q132936|1=Okayama Prefecture}}.

=== Enshrined deities ===
* {{ill|UNKNOWN|WD=Q10936701|lt=Ōmononushi|1=Ōmononushi}} (おおものぬしのかみ)
* {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Sukunahikona|1=UNKNOWN}} (すこなひこなのかみ)
* {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Mihotsuhime|1=UNKNOWN}} (みほつひめのかみ)
* {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Ōanamuchi|1=UNKNOWN}} (おおなむちのかみ)

=== Festivals ===
* New Year Festival: January 1
* Spring Grand Festival: 2nd Sunday of May
* Summer Great Purification Festival: 2nd Sunday of July (ujiko prayer: 2nd Saturday of July)
* Autumn Grand Festival: 3rd Sunday of October (ujiko prayer: 3rd Saturday of October)
* Monthly Festival: 1st day of every month

=== Local information ===
